---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/accounting-precision/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="About Us | TaxPro & Partners"
  description="Empowering businesses through financial integrity — the mission, history, values, and leadership team behind TaxPro & Partners."
  active="about"
  canonicalPath="/templates/accounting-precision/about"
>
<main>
<!-- Hero / Mission -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-tp-xl bg-primary text-on-primary min-h-[500px] md:min-h-[614px] flex items-center">
<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 2px 2px, white 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-tp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop text-center">
<span class="inline-block px-tp-md py-tp-xs bg-secondary text-on-primary rounded-full font-tp-label-sm text-tp-label-sm mb-tp-md tracking-wider">OUR MISSION</span>
<h1 class="font-tp-headline-xl text-tp-headline-lg-mobile md:text-tp-headline-xl mb-tp-md max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-tight">
                    Empowering businesses through financial integrity.
                </h1>
<p class="font-tp-body-lg text-tp-body-lg text-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto opacity-90">
                    We bridge the gap between complex tax regulations and strategic business growth, providing clarity in an ever-changing economic landscape.
                </p>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Our Story / Timeline -->
<section class="py-tp-xl bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-tp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="text-center mb-tp-xl reveal-on-scroll">
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-lg text-tp-headline-lg text-primary mb-2">Our Story</h2>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Decades of navigating financial excellence together.</p>
</div>
<div class="space-y-tp-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
<div class="flex gap-tp-md items-start reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="z-10 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-secondary shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="text-white text-[10px] font-bold">1995</span>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary">The Foundation</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Founded by Arthur Sterling with a vision to modernize corporate tax advisory.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-tp-md items-start reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="z-10 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-secondary shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="text-white text-[10px] font-bold">2010</span>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary">Digital Transformation</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Pioneered cloud-based accounting solutions for high-growth tech enterprises.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-tp-md items-start reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="z-10 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-secondary shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="text-white text-[10px] font-bold">2024</span>
</div>
<div>
<h3 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary">Global Reach</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Now managing over $5B in assets across three continents with a team of 150 experts.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Values -->
<section class="py-tp-xl bg-surface-container-low">
<div class="max-w-tp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="mb-tp-xl text-left max-w-2xl reveal-on-scroll">
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-lg text-tp-headline-lg text-primary mb-2">Our Values</h2>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">The core principles that guide every audit, strategy, and client relationship.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-gutter">
<div class="bg-surface p-tp-lg rounded-xl corporate-shadow flex flex-col border-t-4 border-secondary transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 reveal-on-scroll">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl mb-tp-md">gavel</span>
<h3 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary mb-2">Integrity</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Unyielding adherence to ethical standards and transparent communication in all financial dealings.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface p-tp-lg rounded-xl corporate-shadow flex flex-col border-t-4 border-secondary transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 reveal-on-scroll">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl mb-tp-md">lightbulb</span>
<h3 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary mb-2">Innovation</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Leveraging cutting-edge technology and creative problem-solving to stay ahead of complex regulations.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface p-tp-lg rounded-xl corporate-shadow flex flex-col border-t-4 border-secondary transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 reveal-on-scroll">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl mb-tp-md">verified</span>
<h3 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary mb-2">Excellence</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">A commitment to precision, thoroughness, and delivering superior value to our partners.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Team -->
<section class="py-tp-xl bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-tp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="text-center mb-tp-xl reveal-on-scroll">
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-lg text-tp-headline-lg text-primary mb-2">Leadership Team</h2>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Expertise driven by dedicated professionals.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-gutter">
<div class="group reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-tp-md corporate-shadow relative">
