<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-tp-label-md">Senior Partner</p>
</div>
<div class="group reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-tp-md corporate-shadow relative">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500" alt="Headshot of Elena Rodriguez, Principal Associate." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCuA0zXKL44T7CV2J45LIPg6TNDEzZisxfXUqiGyMb5zYwyl9GB1Zqib33RWEOEIh7zxFyavD-wxvXnWjdfCESNah6jdphjllUQVwiTz-XcuLnoJz0e9UhHfdQ6ASyJbsH08v_fGhHMfk2hiwKBEHtgrPjkVT9NELsI-FMPkLZnwIu7th6cinUih2sI2REIhIkc_maZxlaIjnJ1u3nrjpWnL0srq_R4EI8OZBD2Txfc4S78QhrWCTDbAU5-xejNpyaf-Sz0cDQemAs" />
</div>
<h4 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary">Elena Rodriguez</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-tp-label-md">Principal Associate</p>
</div>
<div class="group reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-tp-md corporate-shadow relative">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500" alt="Headshot of David Chen, Financial Associate." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB4tulI3AHG_-3q0ubKDeclOHOlLfPRNFK1dvOIqUER8DIZFa4GIfvwVkwqCxcJeIkG06mZn8WGXW6BaAygrvMGf49IpjsL5uWrVPOTS7O97Mg3LJry3TsvXd1BAYriNzMjXfQZhybM2gziTDeYvKAN1l71myC0F3A7kmSuUxSn0x3itubEl36HvY8b-OQZgofd9Z0FCLhC5FxDaO-TCCFiSvkRe_dwHV6Di7L0J11QpSkzHAT-2_n2gb6Pv7rTHNB0rycbw7-RV3M" />
</div>
<h4 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md text-primary">David Chen</h4>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-tp-label-md">Financial Associate</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA -->
<section class="py-tp-xl px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-primary-container rounded-2xl p-tp-xl text-center text-on-primary-container corporate-shadow relative overflow-hidden reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-secondary opacity-20 rounded-full -mr-32 -mt-32"></div>
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-lg text-tp-headline-lg mb-tp-md relative z-10 text-white">Ready to secure your financial future?</h2>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md mb-tp-lg relative z-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">Join the hundreds of enterprises that trust TaxPro &amp; Partners for their most critical financial strategies.</p>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-tp-md justify-center relative z-10">
<a href="/templates/accounting-precision/contact" class="bg-secondary text-white px-tp-xl py-tp-md rounded-lg font-tp-label-md text-tp-label-md hover:scale-105 transition-transform inline-block">Schedule Consultation</a>
<a href="/templates/accounting-precision/services" class="border-2 border-secondary-container text-secondary-container px-tp-xl py-tp-md rounded-lg font-tp-label-md text-tp-label-md hover:bg-secondary-container hover:text-on-secondary-container transition-all inline-block">View Our Services</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
</TemplateLayout>
